<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>

<activity xml:id="act-creaTuPropioJuegoDeCarnaval" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Sample responses for a ring toss: <ol>
<li>Ring toss. Stand behind a line and toss 4 rings at 10 different upside down cups.</li>
<li>The person who gets a ring around the most number of cups wins.</li>
</ol>
      </li>
      <li>No response required.</li>
      <li>Sample response: Each upside down cup is now worth different points from 2 to 100. There are 3 marks that are different lengths from the cups. The mark 36 inches from the cup gets you regular points. The mark 72 inches from the cups doubles your points. The mark 108 inches from the cup triples your points.</li>
    </ol>
  </solution>


